	<h3>About IconFORGE</h3>
	<p>IconFORGE is a simple webapp that allows inspecting and building Icon files to use under Windows. This app started as a project to test Javascript capabilities of editing binary files, and as the need to build custom 256px transparency-enabled icons rose, this test became an icon packing app. What this app tries to achieve is to remove the need of downloading extra software when all you want is to simply create an .ico file with a picture of your own. As this app is a product of my spare time, I cannot guarantee any kind of updates or fixes.</p>
	
